1 c. The last date by which the ballots must be postmarked or filed with the
2 commission; and
3 d. Any cattle industry representative may be present at the time the ballots are
4 opened and tabulated.
5 5. The date selected by the commission for the opening and tabulation of the ballots
6 must be at least five days after the date by which the ballots must be postmarked or
